data.description: Price Reduced!! Great Floor Plan!! Charming comes to mind immediately upon seeing this fantastic Ranch home!!  Come see for yourself!! Perfect for a young family or anyone looking for the perfect starter or even if you’re downsizing.   This 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch in Waterford neighborhood in NE Fort Wayne is the ideal first home.  Vaulted ceilings in the en suite Master with 2 other good sized bedrooms means you have plenty of options for more bedrooms or even an office.  If you’re looking for a spot that has plenty of yard for your kids to play sports with friends or just relax to summertime games while you bbq on the grill, this back yard (which backs up to a huge common area) will be perfect for you.  Once you see this home, you’re going to LOVE IT!!   Come take a look today by Scheduling your showing!!
